{"tid":1531811,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"眼鏡撚想問下潛水野","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:16:55.000Z","uid":98416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f449756c26860bf6f4d6a11d9c16297c009804","tid":1531811,"uid":98416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"話說最近鐘意咗潛水，買咗好多潛水裝備，但一路都未買潛水鏡<br />\n因為本人係四眼仔，有冇咩潛水鏡啱四眼仔用? 去迪卡儂試過側邊可能會入水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faab003b5a847d4e61cea9357d661e7cc80ad377","tid":1531811,"uid":32656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"我用scuba pro, 可以配度數鏡"},{"pid":"fdc97706fcb9a1806d313331ff6ac0b3f7aafe59","tid":1531811,"uid":98416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faab003b5a847d4e61cea9357d661e7cc80ad377","tid":1531811,"uid":32656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"我用scuba pro, 可以配度數鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"幾錢，舒唔舒服?<br />\n你知宜家啲潛水裝備幾貴架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6993fc20aa6246fc11e686f7a66f35f0546dd5be","tid":1531811,"uid":32656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"舒服，入唔入水睇下啱唔啱面型同鬆緊較得好唔好，我都試咗幾次先啱<br />\n連埋度數鏡$800（友情價）<br />\n不過好似話因為係水入面睇嘢會放大咗<br />\n所以度數唔使配咁足"},{"pid":"f03175a5429da07d1fdeb3ddc5e5ce3af7998628","tid":1531811,"uid":262346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"時代革命無罪<br />\n<br />\n光復香港有理"},{"pid":"406503ec902a72cb5d59f0e9fb6aca145f97105b","tid":1531811,"uid":112536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"有分單片鏡and 左右兩邊鏡<br />\n理論上單片視野會廣闊啲<br />\n左右兩邊鏡型號可以配有度數鏡片<br />\n有近視唔建議帶Con落水，由其初學又或者training，帶住Con鹽粒砂粒有機會會磨損角膜，不過講係咁講，好多人都會帶Con落水<br />\n<br />\n潛水鏡唔好貪平，始終貼身野，平嘢浸海水膠邊老化